title: Kangana Ranaut in panic mode
text:
Kangana Ranaut is in London to speak at the Women in the World summit, which kicks off today to showcase inspirational stories about women.

Kangana Ranaut 
The actress, however, was taken aback to hear the buzz about her Ketan Mehta-directed biopic, Rani Laxmibai, being shelved.
The actress immediately called up the filmmaker who laughed off the rumours. The National Award winner feels itâ€™s vested interests that are trying to sabotage the project. So, who exactly is Kangs referring to?
